episodes.title: Former Holdeman Minister Lance Dirks Explains the Holdeman Church
episodes.description:
Holdeman is an in depth look at the theology of the Holdeman Mennonite Church through the writings of John Holdeman and testimony of former members.

To check out the documentary: https://youtu.be/JRdJVdY9wBk

To support Last Stand Studios and check out other documentaries: https://laststandstudios.org
subjects: The Church Of God In Christ
